{"tid":541934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無灑水系統 南韓醫院火災37死  韓媒：警鈴響時護士不建議病人逃生","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T06:30:08.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb74d5f1a6df3aab35e49359b6e1eb2fdb0c495","tid":541934,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓慶尚南道密陽市世宗醫院，於昨日（26日）發生大火，釀成37死143傷的慘劇，當地媒體指出，在火災警鈴響起時，至少有一名護士不建議病人採取任何行動，以為警鈴只是故障而已。<br />\n<br />\n據韓國《中央日報》報導，就在警鈴響後幾分鐘內，煙霧就已經瀰漫大樓且電力中斷，病人倉皇從窗戶爬出，靠著消防員架起的梯子逃生，或者跑到屋頂等待直升機救援，一些消防員則設法突破充滿煙霧的火場到達較高的樓層。除了消防單位之外，路人也伸手援助，將罹難者轉送到附近的殯儀館。<br />\n<br />\n另外，世宗醫院並無裝設自動灑水裝置，發生重大傷亡後遭受各方批評。但根據南韓保健福祉部的規定，只有11層樓高、面積600平方公尺的醫療中心需要裝設，而世宗醫院則是5層樓高、面積394.78平方公尺，按照規定不需配備自動灑水器。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpIIwe2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpIIwe2N.jpg&h=f4c12ca0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"918d9dce6f94c8568bca7bb8e7d55eb5444f49cb","tid":541934,"uid":85751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"又人體鍊成"},{"pid":"b51cdadf28499bee0dc38a1c9457787e327f526d","tid":541934,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"又唔好走，似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f6eb63285d3db7c6d1db30e74904ad4748eb79","tid":541934,"uid":38386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"與神同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d771467c7780e116c7cdd7d1da895a95f5cb735e","tid":541934,"uid":47112,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"路人也伸手援助，將罹難者轉送到附近的殯儀館。<br />\n<br />\n真方便"},{"pid":"fdfa047fc53f6ac7a4773fa43f45087ba2894968","tid":541934,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"邪教獻祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdee7eaa4dec3978b4884ca2556aa7418498ced0","tid":541934,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"病人們請瞓低，讓院領導先走"},{"pid":"ffa3ea19d3faf899e173d998167159f441543895","tid":541934,"uid":9412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdfa047fc53f6ac7a4773fa43f45087ba2894968","tid":541934,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"邪教獻祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77eddddac7492bd24c0de10270cf5d6b6721906","tid":541934,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b51cdadf28499bee0dc38a1c9457787e327f526d","tid":541934,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"又唔好走，似曾相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"上次沉船又叫班細路留響房"},{"pid":"0b3fc6db77617b6ebc90aa73bb50192939890ac5","tid":541934,"uid":167426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"次次災難級事故都會有人叫人唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7703ddd398558f80ad6b7bad1f8e68d4448856c0","tid":541934,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3fc6db77617b6ebc90aa73bb50192939890ac5","tid":541934,"uid":167426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"次次災難級事故都會有人叫人唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:01:2